@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Главная";
    
}
<div class="container">
    <script>
        $('[role = search]').addClass("invisible");
    </script>
    <div class="center-block bs-callout bs-callout-danger">
        <center>
            <h3>
                Магазин "Автозапчасти"
            </h3>
        </center>
    </div>
    <div class="center-block bs-callout bs-callout-limegreen">
        <p>Система содержит информацию о <strong>@ViewBag.ProductCount</strong>  товаре(ах), <strong>@ViewBag.CustomerCount</strong> клиенте(ах), <strong>@ViewBag.SupplierCount</strong> организации(ях)-поставщике(ах), <strong>@ViewBag.EmployeeCount</strong> сотруднике(ах) и о <strong>@ViewBag.OrderCount</strong> заказе(ах).</p>
        <p>На @DateTime.Now.ToLongDateString() на складе храниться товаров на общую сумму <strong>@ViewBag.ProductCost</strong> BYN, общим весом<strong> @ViewBag.ProductWeight</strong> кг.</p>

    </div>
    <ul class="nav nav-tabs">
        <li class="active"><a data-toggle="tab" href="#panel1">Заказы</a></li>
        <li><a data-toggle="tab" href="#panel2">Денежные поступления</a></li>
        
    </ul>

    <div class="tab-content">
        <div id="panel1" class="tab-pane fade in active">
            <h3>Заказы (включая НДС):</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>За предыдущий год: <strong>@{int OrderCountLastYear = ViewBag.OrderCountLastYear == null ? 0 : ViewBag.OrderCountLastYear; }@OrderCountLastYear</strong> заказа(ов) на сумму <strong>@{decimal OrderAmountLastYear = ViewBag.OrderAmountLastYear == null ? 0 : ViewBag.OrderAmountLastYear; }@OrderAmountLastYear.ToString("0.000")</strong> BYN.</li>
                <li>За текущий год: <strong>@{int OrderCountYear = ViewBag.OrderCountYear == null ? 0 : ViewBag.OrderCountYear; }@OrderCountYear</strong> заказа(ов) на сумму <strong>@{decimal OrderAmountYear = ViewBag.OrderAmountYear == null ? 0 : ViewBag.OrderAmountYear; }@OrderAmountYear.ToString("0.000")</strong> BYN.</li>

                <li>За предыдущий месяц: <strong>@{int OrderCountLastMonth = ViewBag.OrderCountLastMonth == null ? 0 : ViewBag.OrderCountLastMonth; }@OrderCountLastMonth</strong> заказа(ов) на сумму <strong>@{decimal OrderAmountLastMonth = ViewBag.OrderAmountLastMonth == null ? 0 : ViewBag.OrderAmountLastMonth; }@OrderAmountLastMonth.ToString("0.000")</strong> BYN.</li>
                <li>За текущий месяц: <strong>@{int OrderCountMonth = ViewBag.OrderCountMonth == null ? 0 : ViewBag.OrderCountMonth; }@OrderCountMonth</strong> заказа(ов) на сумму <strong>@{decimal OrderAmountMonth = ViewBag.OrderAmountMonth == null ? 0 : ViewBag.OrderAmountMonth; }@OrderAmountMonth.ToString("0.000")</strong> BYN.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div id="panel2" class="tab-pane fade">
            <h3>Денежные поступления:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>За предыдущий год: <strong>@{int ReceiptCountLastYear = ViewBag.ReceiptCountLastYear == null ? 0 : ViewBag.ReceiptCountLastYear; }@ReceiptCountLastYear</strong> поступление(й) на сумму <strong>@{decimal ReceiptAmountLastYear = ViewBag.ReceiptAmountLastYear == null ? 0 : ViewBag.ReceiptAmountLastYear; }@ReceiptAmountLastYear.ToString("0.000")</strong> BYN.</li>
                <li>За текущий год: <strong>@{int ReceiptCountYear = ViewBag.ReceiptCountYear == null ? 0 : ViewBag.ReceiptCountYear; }@ReceiptCountYear</strong> поступление(й) на сумму <strong>@{decimal ReceiptAmountYear = ViewBag.ReceiptAmountYear == null ? 0 : ViewBag.ReceiptAmountYear; }@ReceiptAmountYear.ToString("0.000")</strong> BYN.</li>

                <li>За предыдущий месяц: <strong>@{int ReceiptCountLastMonth = ViewBag.ReceiptCountLastMonth == null ? 0 : ViewBag.ReceiptCountLastMonth; }@ReceiptCountLastMonth</strong> поступление(й) на сумму <strong>@{decimal ReceiptAmountLastMonth = ViewBag.ReceiptAmountLastMonth == null ? 0 : ViewBag.ReceiptAmountLastMonth; }@ReceiptAmountLastMonth.ToString("0.000")</strong> BYN.</li>
                <li>За текущий месяц: <strong>@{int ReceiptCountMonth = ViewBag.ReceiptCountMonth == null ? 0 : ViewBag.ReceiptCountMonth; }@ReceiptCountMonth</strong> поступление(й) на сумму <strong>@{decimal m21 = ViewBag.o2m1 == null ? 0 : ViewBag.o2m1; }@m21.ToString("0.000")</strong> BYN.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
    </div>

</div>